Package model

Class BibliographicProduct

java.lang.Object
model.BibliographicProduct
Direct Known Subclasses:
Book, Magazine
public abstract class BibliographicProduct extends Object
The abstract class representing a bibliographic product. It provides common attributes and methods for books and magazines.
